content: ['// SPDX-License-Identifier: MITpragma solidity ^0.8.17;contract EtherWallet {    address payable public owner;    constructor() {        owner = payable(msg.sender);    }    receive() external payable {}    function withdraw(uint _amount) external {        require(msg.sender == owner, "caller is not owner");        payable(msg.sender).transfer(_amount);    }    function getBalance() external view returns (uint) {        return address(this).balance;    }}']
